WEBVTT

00:02:29.417 --> 00:02:32.101
by fixing our dilapidated hospitals

00:02:32.125 --> 00:02:34.268
and building us new ones.

00:02:34.292 --> 00:02:35.726
But what did he do?

00:02:35.750 --> 00:02:40.684
He spends three months
receiving treatment in London in 2017.

00:02:40.708 --> 00:02:44.184
We were without a president
for three months.

00:02:44.208 --> 00:02:46.226
We were president-less for three months.

00:02:46.250 --> 00:02:48.934
So then it becomes my job
to call out the President,

00:02:48.958 --> 00:02:50.226
with respect, of course.

00:02:50.250 --> 00:02:53.559
I said, "Ha, Mr. President,
it's your girl, Adeola.

00:02:53.583 --> 00:02:55.559
You know how I do, 
how you doing?

00:02:55.583 --> 00:02:57.434
You have no shame."

00:02:57.458 --> 00:02:58.768
I forgot to add "sir."

00:02:58.792 --> 00:03:00.893
"Sir, you have no shame.